name: podamShouldCreateInstancesOfGenericPojosWithFactoryMethodsWhenTheConcreteTypeIsKnown

testSteps.description: When I invoke the factory manufacturing for class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.FactoryInstantiablePojo with specific types {class java.util.Date}
Then the pojo uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.FactoryInstantiablePojoImpl@a11079 must be of the type class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.FactoryInstantiablePojo
Then the pojo Fri Oct 20 17:32:43 IST 2017 must be of the type class java.util.Date

title: Podam should be able to create instances of generic POJOs with factory methods when the concrete type is known
